# 14. 大きく育つ想い

Miku: Huh...? We're back...?
Rin: Yeah, we are! I wish I could've stayed a little longer...
Luka: Hehe. Me too. But it was nice to see what that SEKAI was like back then.
Luka: I didn't realize just how long those other versions of us had been watching over everyone.
Rin: Yeah, they were all doing their best to make sure everyone would discover their true feelings!
MEIKO: And coming up with ways to help support them.
Len: They were working really hard to make sure they'd be there for everyone when that time came.
KAITO: Not being able to get the others to realize that SEKAI existed did become a little frustrating at times.
Miku: But they kept doing their best to help everyone despite their struggles.
Miku: And they've become a huge source of support.
Miku: Then and now, including this very moment...
Miku: Oh, this light...
MEIKO: That just now...
Len: Did the sprouts in their SEKAI just grow bigger...?!
Luka: This must also be one of SEKAI's powers.
KAITO: Yes, but... What kind of plant do you think they are?
Miku: What if they're...?
Rin: Oh, it's flashing again...!
Luka: Oh...
Rin: Woooow!! This place is so pretty!
MEIKO: Where are we? It doesn't look like anyone's SEKAI.
Miku: ...
Miku: This could be a new SEKAI that was collectively born out of all of their feelings.
KAITO: All of their feelings?
Miku: Yes. I've actually been here before.
Miku: You need to see this tree! Everyone's feelings are hanging from it.
Len: Whoa, you're right...! And they all involve different things...!
Luka: Is this a CD...? Oh, it's Leo/need's debut single.
Rin: I found some pictures of Minori and the others, and some of their merch!
Len: Check it out, MEIKO! There's a flyer for RAD BLAST!
KAITO: I'm finding posters Tsukasa and his troupe made for their shows as well.
Miku: There's a pile of sheet music over here... Oh, and some apples.
KAITO: There really are a lot of things hanging from this tree. And they're all clear representations of everyone's feelings.
MEIKO: So, Miku, this tree...
Miku: Yes. Their feelings, along with ours, made it grow this big.
Rin: Really...?!
Rin: Actually, when you look at it as a whole, it does feel like we overcame a lot together to help make their dreams come true. That makes me really happy!
Miku: Hehe. Me too.
Miku: And it's grown so much since the last time I was here.
Miku: That must be a reflection of just how much everyone else has grown.
Luka: It's growing with them...? That's so wonderful.
Len: Yeah, it is! Also, that means it's gonna keep growing bigger and bearing more fruits!
MEIKO: Hehe. I'll definitely be looking forward to seeing that.
Miku: Me too!
Miku: (This is so nice...)
Miku: (A SEKAI made out of everybody's feelings... And it changes little by little as they grow.)
Miku: (I wonder what's going to happen here moving forward.)
Miku: (I can't say for certain right now...)
Miku: But I'd like to keep watching over them...!
